the rising Sun, ...

3
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:50,480
...for it's the source of light
for the whole world.

4
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:55,040
But dad, the Sun gives us light
only during the day.

5
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:58,480
But the nights are lit up in
the city, isn't that so, Daddy?

6
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:01,880
Do people in the city pray to
the lights ofthe night?

7
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:09,080
People in the city pray for wealth;
not for the light ofthe day.

8
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:12,880
And those who are enamored of
wealth live a life of lies...

9
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,480
... and they oRen stray
towards the wrong path.

10
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:16,200
Why so, Daddy?

11
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:19,480
Because the path oftruth
is difficult to tread upon.

12
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,240
lt is a fiey path.

13
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:26,000
