is coming to our village!

39
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,880
This is Mr. Mathur,
the chief engineer.

40
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,280
Greetings, Sir.- He's here for
the electricity project.

41
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:08,760
Till the project is completed,
he'll stay as a guest in our house.

42
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,760
Please come inside, Mr.Mathur.
- Thank you.

43
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:16,000
Electricity will bring about...

44
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:20,280
... a renaissance of a new
India in our village.

45
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:22,160
Oh yes.
- Please come along.

46
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,080
This is the school
for the children.

47
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,280
lt's necessay to have
electricity in here.

48
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:31,880
Hey lady! What are you doing?!
Is that a garbage dump?

49
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:36,080
That must be a hat you're wearing!
- Yes.

50
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:39,160
You're well-regarded here,
school master.

51
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,480
The people not only respect me
but also love me.

52
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,120
Bloody swine!

53
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:50,760
Have you gotten drunk again?
- Yes, l am drunk!

54
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:54,960
Bloody swine!

55
00:03:57,599 --> 00:04:01,080
You told my wife
not to give me money...

56
