village.

73
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:40,480
l know! The winds of progress
are picking up force.

74
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:45,880
l must get a hold on my fiefs.
Else, l'll be blown away.

75
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:33,080
The money l've given you,
Dinkar Rao...

76
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,080
... was issued by the
government of India.

77
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,160
lt's worth far more...

78
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:44,640
... than the scrap of paper
you're given me in exchange.

79
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:57,840
You've tried to sell me the lands
which belong to the villagers.

80
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:04,440
You see, Sir...- Enough of it.
You may keep the money.

81
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,920
l don't take back what l have
given.

82
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:12,840
My principle is profit.
For the sake of profit, l will...

83
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:16,400
... even accept a lie as the truth.
And l'll make friends of my enemies.

84
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:21,440
Get that?- Forgive me for
having told lies.

85
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,920
But you didn't tell
me the truth, either.

86
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:29,320
You didn't tell me that you
want to use this place for...

87
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,840
...smuggling and dealing in
stuff like opium and hashish.

88
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,440
You're right.

89
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:49,760
This village ofyours, Mandwa,
is nowhere on the map of India.

90
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:54,320
This place is close to Bombay; and yet
it is beyond the reach of Indian laws.

91
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:57,400
This place is ideally suited
for my shady business.

92
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:01,440
l hear that a schoolmaster
in this village...

93
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,440
... is tying to get
electricity in here.

94
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:08,440
lf anything like that happens
l'll be sorely disappointed.

95
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:12,920
And, it'll cost you your life.
Get that?

96
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,440
The schoolmaster!

97
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:46,440
ls that the result of my untiring
efforts in tying to educate you?

98
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:51,440
l had told you about
the mother in evey woman.

99
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:54,600
And here you are... with a
prostitute! In this hell!

100
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,440
Get out of here before ...

101
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:05,440
... your character is
destroyed. Get out!

102
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:14,080
You've destroyed many homes.

103
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,080
You've destroyed many young
lives.

104
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:21,000
And now, you're dragging
the children into sin.

105
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:27,160
You should be ashamed ofyourself.
- Why must l be ashamed?

106
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,960
Brothels are the creation of men.

107
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:35,760
They push helpless women
into prostitution.

108
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:39,160
Stop talking nonsense!
Only a fool...

109
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:45,160
... would step into
this world of sin.

110
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:50,440
lt's easy for you to preach,
because you aren't involved.

111
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,440
lfyou're man enough, ...

112
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:57,440
... you will help me out
ofthis world of sin.

113
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:06,800
lfyou really are man enough, you'll
bring in these books ofyours...

114
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,840
... and tell me of
the good and the evil.

115
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,200
''lfyou're man enough...

116
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:17,000
... you will help me out
ofthis world of sin.''

117
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,920
Haven't you been able
to memorise the alphabet yet!

118
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:24,560
Please don't hurt her, Daddy. It's my
fault. l didn't teach her properly.

119
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,480
l've been irresponsible.
Beat me ifyou will.

120
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:49,200
Do you want to take a punishment
for your sister's fault?

121
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:56,200
You have told me that l must
stand the test of fire.

122
00:10:56,879 --> 00:11:01,240
And that l must pick up
someone else's burden too.

123
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,800
Well said, Son.

124
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,600
You have taught me ...

125
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:15,160
... the vey lesson l taught you.

126
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:33,600
You want to take your
Iessons over here, don't you?

127
00:11:35,039 --> 00:11:39,840
l accept the responsibilities of
teaching you, from now onwards.

128
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:47,080
Drop your airs! Your father spent
the last night at the brothel.

129
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,800
Eveyone in the village has
seen him there. Understand?

130
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,600
Did you hit him?
- Yes.

131
00:12:00,919 --> 00:12:05,320
Why?
Apologise to him. Go on!

132
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:08,720
l won't apologise.
- Won't you?!

133
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,400
The schoolmaster must...

134
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:25,320
... Iose his esteem
and social standing tonight.

135
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:30,760
And, tomorrow morning,
he must walk in disgrace.

136
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:35,160
He must be a broken man by tomorrow.
And he may never raise his head again.

137
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,600
lt will be done.

138
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:42,800
Please don't visit
the brothel anymore.

139
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:51,240
Those who tread upon the path of
truth do not care for wagging tongues.

140
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:56,320
The lamp must be lit...

141
00:12:57,440 --> 00:13:00,280
... by fire to dispel the darkness.

142
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:06,600
There goes the schoolmaster.-
He isn't as innocent as he seems.

143
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:19,000
