- What a shame!

152
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,680
We respected him. And this is what
he turns out to be!

153
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:13,600
Get up, you hypocrite!
- Drag that shameless fellow out!

154
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,520
Burn the master's house.

155
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:23,600
Father...
- Vijay...

156
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,320
Father...

157
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:08,600
This is the path through fire.

158
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:10,840
No...

159
00:16:02,759 --> 00:16:04,160
