160
00:16:06,879 --> 00:16:08,640
You have killed him.

161
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,480
You have killed the
school master.

162
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:22,160
He cared for you as long as he
lived. And now you've killed him!

163
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:27,600
No one even cares for his
corpse.

164
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:33,000
Swine! Cowards! Fools! Animals!

165
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,000
There goes schoolmaster
Dinanath.

166
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:16,640
What are you staring at Vijay?
Don't even look at that village.

167
00:17:17,039 --> 00:17:19,480
Forget that you were born over
there.

168
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:23,640
No! l will never forget that
village.

169
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:31,600
Some day, l'll give that village
to my mother.

170
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,640
So you've received your pay.
- Yes, Sir.

171
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:13,360
Now get lost. We're going to
ambush Kancha Cheena.

172
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,600
Return to your beat aRer 1 hour.
- All right

173
00:18:15,039 --> 00:18:17,240
