- Take that..... and that.

176
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,920
And make sure you don't foul up.
Now get going.

177
00:18:50,519 --> 00:18:51,600
The dog! He escaped.
- The swine escaped us!

178
00:18:51,839 --> 00:18:53,800
How did he find out?

179
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:35,200
From now on, this is our
home, Mummy.

180
00:19:36,319 --> 00:19:37,800
This is where we are going to
live.

181
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:51,800
Get out!
Greetings, Sir.

182
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,400
The merchandise arrives tonight.
Take care of it.

183
00:19:56,119 --> 00:19:57,400
Let's move.

184
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:05,360
(He was) Kancha Cheena.

185
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:25,960
Come...

186
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,560
Come...

187
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:34,960
Come inside..

188
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:48,440
What happened?...Mother...

189
00:20:56,599 --> 00:20:58,440
Don't beat him.
- Move away..

190
00:21:03,359 --> 00:21:04,360
l have taken down your complaint,
haven't l?

191
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:07,960
When are you going to arrest the
manager ofthe petrol pump?

192
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:09,680
l know vey well what
l'm supposed to do!

193
00:21:09,799 --> 00:21:12,960
l've been in this job for 10 years.
And now, you're tying to teach me!

194
00:21:13,079 --> 00:21:16,960
Get out of here!- Bloody cop!
And you do take bribes.

195
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:22,920
Did you hear that?!
That boy talks too much!

196
00:21:23,039 --> 00:21:24,840
Wonder what he'll make
when he grows up.

197
00:21:58,559 --> 00:22:03,400
We've found out about
the fellow who burnt...

198
00:22:03,519 --> 00:22:06,120
... Kancha Cheena's petrol pump.
- Who is he?

199
00:22:06,559 --> 00:22:09,440
A melve-year old boy.

200
00:22:09,599 --> 00:22:12,120
A 12-year old!!
- A vey smart kid.

201
00:22:13,119 --> 00:22:17,200
He set the petrol pump afire to
avenge his insult to his mother.

202
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:21,280
What a kid!
- Say what Usman...

203
00:22:21,519 --> 00:22:25,200
Let's bail the kid out and
put him to work for us.

204
00:22:25,519 --> 00:22:30,400
You'd rather think it over.
The boy is much too spirited.

205
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:34,960
He could wipe us out once he
grows up.

206
00:22:35,519 --> 00:22:37,560
Wrong, Shem.

207
00:22:37,839 --> 00:22:42,360
Help him out now and he'll
remain a faithful dog forever.

208
00:22:43,519 --> 00:22:45,280
Go on, Terence..... take a
decision.

209
00:22:45,519 --> 00:22:48,800
Bail the boy out and we're one up on
our opponent. Do you get that Shem?

210
00:22:49,119 --> 00:22:51,400
Get him offthe hook.- And
he'll remain faithful forever.

211
00:22:53,519 --> 00:22:57,400
Fathead Shem won't understand!
- All right... do what you please.

212
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:01,280
Do you know that it's a crime to
set petrol pumps on fire?

213
00:23:02,119 --> 00:23:04,880
And what was it that had
been done to my mother?

214
00:23:05,519 --> 00:23:06,640
Wasn't that a crime?

215
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,400
You could've lodged a complaint
at the police station.

216
00:23:10,079 --> 00:23:12,720
ls that so?
Well, l did that.

217
00:23:13,519 --> 00:23:16,440
l did report it.
But what did you do about it?

218
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:21,120
Nothing. You did nothing at all.
And that's why l did it.

219
00:23:21,960 --> 00:23:25,120
l burnt it... l burnt the petrol
pump.

220
00:23:25,519 --> 00:23:29,280
What's your name?
Vijay Dinanath Chauhan.

221
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,800
That's my full name.

222
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:37,400
Dinanath Chavan was my father.
My mother is Suhasini Chauhan.

223
00:23:39,319 --> 00:23:41,040
l'm from the village of Mandwa.

224
00:23:43,519 --> 00:23:48,800
l'm 36 years, 9 months
and 2 days old...

225
00:23:49,079 --> 00:23:51,800
... and 16 hours as of now.

226
00:23:53,319 --> 00:23:57,400
Won't you mend you ways?
- And why should l?

227
00:23:59,839 --> 00:24:02,280
The world is a bad
place, Mr Gaitonde.

228
00:24:04,599 --> 00:24:07,800
One must be crooked to
survive in this world.

229
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:12,400
Anyone who mends his ways, is
bound to die. Did you know that?

230
00:24:13,519 --> 00:24:15,960
Keep the advice for your
underlings in your hutments.

231
00:24:18,079 --> 00:24:21,640
Your underlings worship you.
You are the Godfather.

232
00:24:23,119 --> 00:24:24,880
